  <description><![CDATA[<p>Location is key on a ski holiday and it doesn't get much better than the Hotel Hermitage. It overlooks the slopes on the main ski run back to the village, making it a perfect ski-in/ski-out base. Inside, the hotel is fairly basic but you'll find pretty much everything you need.</p>
<p>Venturing into town is an easy two-minute walk before you reach the cobbled high street. Here you'll find plenty of shops and some great places to enjoy the fantastic après on offer. After a drink or two in town, head back to the hotel to fill up on the hearty evening meal before a good night’s sleep to do it all again the following day.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour 30 mins by coach from Turin airport.</p>]]></description>
